data.description: Check out this beautiful maintained two family in the town of Raynham. Perfect for owner occupied, or an investor. spacious yard with two driveways. Each unit has private entrances. First unit boasts two spacious bedrooms, living room with hardwood floors throughout, updated eat-in kitchen with new counters, and full bath/in unit access to the basement with laundry hookup. The second unit has large living room with hardwood floors, full bath, three bedrooms and eat-in kitchen with attic access to the third floor with a spacious bedroom. Beautiful corner lot conveniently located to shopping and easy access to highways. DONT MISS OUT ON THE GEM!
